==English==

===Noun phrase===
'''[[item]] of [[furniture]]''' (''plural'' '''items of furniture''')

# Any item, such as a table or cupboard, that consistutes furniture.

====Usage notes====
'''Item of furniture''' is used as a singular of the [[mass noun]] '''[[furniture]]''', which has no singular of its own.

====Synonyms====
*[[piece of furniture]]

====Translations====
*Dutch: [[meubel]] ''n'', [[meubelstuk]] ''n''
*French: [[meuble]] ''m''
*Spanish: [[mueble]] ''m''

